---
layout: page
title: Healthcheck questionnaire
subtitle: Assess where you’re up to
intro: |
  Our healthcheck questionnaire is designed to help you through through all key aspects of your scheme, and helps us understand how we can help you make it happen.
icon: start
---
{% import "forms.njk" as forms %}

<form name="kent_health_check" netlify>

  <h2>Lead contact</h2>

  {{ forms.input('contact_name', label='Full name', hint='Applicant name including title') }}
  {{ forms.textarea('contact_address', label='Address', hint='Applicant address including postcode') }}
  {{ forms.input('contact_phone_mobile', label='Phone number (mobile)') }}
  {{ forms.input('contact_phone_landline', label='Phone number (landline)') }}
  {{ forms.input('contact_email', type="email", label='Email address', required="true") }}
  {{ forms.boolean('contact_permission', label='Are you happy for us to contact you to follow up on your responses above?') }}
  {{ forms.boolean('mailing_list', label='Do you want to be added to our mailing list?') }}

  <h2>Group information</h2>
  <h3>Basic information</h3>

  {{ forms.input('group_name', label='Full name of group') }}
  {{ forms.select(
    'number_of_members',
    label='Number of members',
    options=['Just me','2 to 5 people','6 to 10 people','11 to 20 people','20+ people']
    )
  }}
  {{ forms.input('group_founding_date', label='When was it set up?') }}
  {{ forms.select(
    'type_of_group',
    label='Type of group',
    options=['Not formally constituted yet','Co-operative for the benefit of its members','Community Benefit Society','Company Limited by Guarantee','Don’t know yet and would like your help with this','Other (please specify)']
    )
  }}
  {{ forms.input('further_information_about_group_type', label='Additional information about type of group') }}
  {{ forms.textarea('registered_address', label='Registered address of group') }}
  {{ forms.boolean('bank_account_setup', label='Does the group already have a bank account?') }}
  {{ forms.input('website', label='Website') }}
  {{ forms.textarea('social_media_accounts', label='Social media accounts', hint='If the group has any social media accounts please provide links to them.') }}

  <h3>Your setup</h3>
  {{ forms.textarea('skills', label='Relevant skills within your group', hint='Provide a brief description of the background, skills and abilities of any individuals in the group that will be of benefit to your scheme.') }}
  {{ forms.textarea('time', label='Time currently being spent working on scheme', hint='How much time do you estimate your group is spending working towards the objectives of this scheme?') }}
  {{ forms.textarea('democratic_process', label='How are (or will) you engaging your local community?', hint='How have you, or how will you, engage other members of the local community in terms of a) giving their support to and/or b) being actively involved in your scheme?') }}

  <h2>Scheme information</h2>

  <h3>Basic information</h3>
  {{ forms.input('scheme_name', label='Name of scheme', hint='If known at this time') }}
  {{ forms.input('scheme_location', label='Location of scheme', hint='State town or village if known') }}
  {{ forms.input('scheme_local_authority', label='Local authority', hint='The local authority responsible for the location and surrounding area(s)') }}

  {{ forms.select(
    'land_acquisition',
    label='How do you hope to acquire land or a building for your scheme?',
    options=[ 'Purchase on the open market',
              'Use property already owned by our group',
              'Lease/rent',
              'Seek asset transfer',
              'Buy at a discount',
              'Section 106 deal with the local authority',
              'Don’t know yet and would like your help with this',
              'Other (please specify)'
            ]
    )
  }}
  {{ forms.input('further_information_about_acquisition', label='Further information about acquisition plans') }}

  {{ forms.select(
    'site_location',
    label='Have you already identified a specific site within the location for your scheme?',
    options=[ 'We would like help finding a site/building',
              'We haven’t looked at any sites/buildings',
              'We’ve looked but haven’t selected a site/building',
              'We’ve found a site we like but haven’t acquired it',
              'We’ve acquired a site',
              'We’ve acquired a site and outline planning permission',
              'We’ve acquired a site and full planning permission',
              'Other (please specify)'
            ]
    )
  }}
  {{ forms.input('further_information_about_site_location', label='Further information about site location') }}


  <h3>Awareness and support</h3>
  {{ forms.textarea('local_authority_officers', label='Are any local authority officers aware of your scheme?', hint='List any officers aware of your scheme and state whether they support or oppose your plans') }}
  {{ forms.textarea('local_councillors', label='Are any local councillors aware of your scheme?', hint='List any councillors aware of your scheme and state whether they support or oppose your plans') }}
  {{ forms.textarea('other_local_authority_awareness', label='Are any other people in your local authority aware of your scheme?', hint='List anyone working for your local authority who is aware of your scheme, their role and whether they support or oppose your plans') }}

  <h3>Local housing needs and potential scheme benefits</h3>
  <p>We’d like to understand why you want to deliver your proposed scheme so please provide a brief description of:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>the local community as a whole</li>
    <li>the housing situation or housing shortage within that local community</li>
    <li>the residents your scheme will serve</li>
    <li>any economic difficulties that exist within the residents your scheme will serve</li>
    <li>anything else you think we should be aware of</li>
  </ul>

  {{ forms.textarea('local_community_profile', label='Local community profile') }}
  {{ forms.textarea('local_housing_situation', label='Local housing situation') }}
  {{ forms.textarea('scheme_beneficiaries', label='Scheme beneficiaries') }}
  {{ forms.textarea('scheme_beneficiary_economic_situation', label='Economic situation of beneficiaries') }}
  {{ forms.textarea('other_useful_information', label='Other useful information') }}

  <h3>Housing details</h3>
  {{ forms.checkbox(
    'scheme_type',
    label='What type of housing scheme will it be?',
    hint='<a target="_blank" href="https://www.communityledhomes.org.uk/types-of-community-led-housing">See a description of each type</a> (opens in new window)',
    options=[ 'Co-housing',
              'Self-help',
              'Self-build',
              'Custom build',
              'Community land trust',
              'Mutual home ownership',
              'Co-operative',
              'Don’t know yet and would like your help with this',
              'Other (please specify)'
            ]
    )
  }}
  {{ forms.input('further_information_about_scheme', label='Further information about the type of scheme') }}

  {{ forms.textarea('description_of_housing', label='Provide a brief description of the type of housing you think is needed', hint='Details to include: a) if they are flats, bungalows or terraced/semi-detached/detached properties b) if they are for a specific sector of the local community c) if it is a new build or a refurbishment / repurposing of an existing building d) whether or not they are to be constructed and will run in an environmentally friendly and sustainable way') }}
  {{ forms.checkbox(
    'type_of_tenure',
    label='Have you decided what kind of tenure you want to provide?',
    options=[ 'Don’t know yet and would like your help with this',
              'Owner occupier',
              'Shared ownership',
              'Social rent',
              'Private rented',
              'Affordable rent (e.g. 80% of market rate)',
              'Other (please specify)'
            ]
    )
  }}
  {{ forms.input('further_information_about_tenure_type', label='Further information about tenure type') }}

  {{ forms.select(
    'management_arrangements',
    label='Intended management arrangements',
    options=['We want to manage the homes ourselves','We want a third party to manage the homes, such as a housing association','Don’t know and we would like your help with this','Other (please specify)']
    )
  }}

  {{ forms.boolean('business_plan_and_budget', label='Have you started or completed a business plan and outline budget?') }}
  {{ forms.textarea('nearby_groups', label='Are you aware of any nearby groups proposing community-led housing?', hint='If you are aware of any groups, please list them and state if you are intending to collaborate with them.') }}

  <h2>Scheme timescales</h2>
  {{ forms.input('scheme_start_date', label='When would you like to start your build or refurbishment?', hint='If your scheme has already started, provide the approximate start date.') }}
  {{ forms.input('scheme_end_date', label='When are you aiming to finish your build or refurbishment?') }}

  <h2>Scheme partners</h2>

  {{ forms.checkbox(
    'partners',
    label='Are you working with (or planning to work with) any of the following types of partners?',
    options=[ 'A large, volume housebuilder',
              'A small or medium sized builder',
              'Registered provider (housing association)',
              'An existing community organisation',
              'A local authority',
              'We want to do it alone',
              'Don’t know yet and would like your help with this',
              'Other (please specify)'
            ]
    )
  }}

  {{ forms.input('further_information_about_partners', label='Further information about partners') }}

  <h2>Finance</h2>
  {{ forms.checkbox(
    'finance',
    label='How are you financing the scheme?',
    options=[ 'We have all the money we need',
              'We have some of the money we need',
              'We intend to raise money through loans',
              'We intend to raise money through grants',
              'We intend to raise money through donations',
              'Don’t know yet and would like your help with this'
            ]
    )
  }}

  <h2>Additional information</h2>
  {{ forms.textarea('additional_information', label='Is there any further information you want to provide?') }}
  {{ forms.textarea('additional_help', label='Is there anything else you would like us to help you with?') }}

  <button class="button" type="submit">Submit</button>

</form>


